OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day. Sunny and chilly to
OL,6,Fstart, but cloud will begin to bubble
OL,7,Fup during the afternoon, with some
OL,8,Fsunny intervals at times. Light winds,
OL,9,Ffeeling warm in the sun.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloud breaking through the
OL,12,Fevening, with some late sunny spells.
OL,13,FPartly cloudy overnight, with a chance
OL,14,Fof isolated light showers. Light winds
OL,15,Fcontinuing. Cold with a risk of frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
