OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA cold and rather bright
OL,6,Fstart. Becoming increasingly cloudy
OL,7,Fthrough the morning. Occasional
OL,8,Fshowers will move slowly west in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Winds remaining largely
OL,10,Flight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,13,Fwith sunny spells Tuesday and
OL,14,FWednesday. Cloudy start Thursday,
OL,15,Fclearing later. Breezy, especially
OL,16,Fover hills. Warm, though cooler near
OL,17,Fcoasts. Chilly by night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
